Product Description

Nazar Suraksha Kawach means the "evil eye bead" is actually a stone bead which is worn to protect oneself from evil looks. The stone is an amalgamation of molten glass iron copper water and salt. This particular combination of minerals and metals is believed to provide a shield from the forces of evil. The Nazar Suraksha Kawach has the symbol of an eye worked upon it. The symbol of the eye is regarded as a potent amulet for protection against evil forces in almost every culture of the world like Jewish Islamic Hindu Buddhist and Christian. Thus in Turkey you have an eye for an eye.Â  NSK help in removing negative influences in ones life. These amulets and talismans are considered to be powerful tools which help in protection against bad and negative effects in ones life. The NSK gives protection and brings luck to all. Have you just had a new child or bought a new car or built a new office building or worried that your "friends" and others are jealous of your good fortune? Then this is the product which is meant for protecting you and your family members from all these worries. The bead reflects the evil intent back to the onlooker. It somewhat resembles an eye and it is said the typical blue color is a factor in protecting the use.

Product Description

Nazar Suraksha Kawach means the "evil eye bead" is actually a stone bead which is worn to protect oneself from evil looks. The stone is an amalgamation of molten glass iron copper water and salt. This particular combination of minerals and metals is believed to provide a shield from the forces of evil. The Nazar Suraksha Kawach has the symbol of an eye worked upon it. The symbol of the eye is regarded as a potent amulet for protection against evil forces in almost every culture of the world like Jewish Islamic Hindu Buddhist and Christian. Thus in Turkey you have an eye for an eye.Â  NSK help in removing negative influences in ones life. These amulets and talismans are considered to be powerful tools which help in protection against bad and negative effects in ones life. The NSK gives protection and brings luck to all. Have you just had a new child or bought a new car or built a new office building or worried that your "friends" and others are jealous of your good fortune? Then this is the product which is meant for protecting you and your family members from all these worries. The bead reflects the evil intent back to the onlooker. It somewhat resembles an eye and it is said the typical blue color is a factor in protecting the use.
